<i>The Challenge.</i>

1308
02:37:20,724 --> 02:37:22,483
<i>The Searchers.</i>

1309
02:37:25,843 --> 02:37:28,158
<i>Magnificent Obsession.</i>

1310
02:37:30,382 --> 02:37:32,221
